Affiliates | Seventy Seven Energy






































































Affiliates









Drill Faster. Safer. Smarter.
Nomac Drilling provides premium drilling services for oil and natural gas operators throughout the most active onshore U.S. oil and natural gas plays including the Anadarko and Permian basins and the Eagle Ford, Haynesville, Marcellus, Utica and Niobrara shales. Our all-electric fleet features AC electric drives, high spec top drives and 7,500 psi mud pumps. Almost all of our fleet is multi-well pad capable with the majority of such rigs utilizing state-of-the-art “walking” technologies.
Visit Nomac’s website at nomacdrilling.com.
 






Unlocking America’s Energy
Performance Technologies performs pressure-pumping services in Ohio, Oklahoma and Texas, with plans for future expansion into other areas. The company is headquartered in El Reno, Oklahoma.
Visit the Performance Technologies website at performancetech.com.






Innovation and efficiency
Great Plains Oilfield Rental supplies high-quality tools and services to the oil and natural gas industry, including:

Drill pipe
Drill collars
Frac tanks
Water transfer
Air drilling
Mud tanks/mud systems
Flow back

Visit the Great Plains Oilfield Rental website at gpor.com.

































 



About | Seventy Seven Energy






































































About






What Is Seventy Seven Energy?

On April 20, 2017, Seventy Seven Energy and its affiliate companies were acquired by Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc. SSE is a diversified oilfield services company that provides a wide range of wellsite services and equipment to U.S. land-based exploration and production (“E&P”) customers operating in unconventional resource plays. Through our umbrella of affiliates, we provide comprehensive upstream services, including drilling, pressure pumping and oilfield rental tools. Our operations are geographically diversified across many of the most active oil and natural gas plays in the onshore United States.
Our Affiliates

Great Plains Oilfield Rental
Nomac Drilling
Performance Technologies

Our Commitment
As a best-in-class oilfield services company, we are committed to our customers and their every need. Seventy Seven Energy delivers world-class technology, operational efficiency and proven industry experience to equip our customers with sustainable competitive advantage.






























 



